{"tid":2021502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你哋有冇諗過你地父母根本冇諗過要你（長文慎入）","createTime":"2020-05-17T18:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T08:36:34.000Z","uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a96b0e6f4c350eca74b4d774c5e6ee4253bd2427","tid":2021502,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:44:45.000Z","msg":"交代少少背景<br />\n由細到大父母都冇乜理過你，表面上供書教學，但係其實佢地根本唔想浪費錢喺你身上，望住隔離啲同學仔日日放學去補習，溫書，學呢樣學嗰樣，但相反你自己日日都戇鳩鳩咁過。屋企唔大，得兩間房，由細到大佢都冇諗過比一間房你自己，佢覺得應該靠你自己去搵錢，而唔係靠佢哋。但試問喺宜家呢個物質社會，想搵錢買樓租樓根本冇可能嘅事更何況我都未出身。你地只係佢生命中嘅一件過客，泄欲完之後一件垃圾。 衣家好想死。我知道係而家呢個時候開啲咁嘅post係好唔啱，但我真係希望大家諗吓你係佢心目中係啲咩。最後光復香港，時代革命。sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398d3f492449d71af7691017b977c58f98e34123","tid":2021502,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2d78bd48a9c